<div class="thumbinner" style="width:182px;"><a href="/wiki/File:500000000000_dinars.jpg" class="image" title="Yugoslavia 500 billion Dinar bank note"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/9/97/500000000000_dinars.jpg/180px-500000000000_dinars.jpg" width="180" height="90" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
