<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Hyperinflation&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9" title="Edit section: Further reading">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Further reading</span></h2>
<div class="references-small" style="margin-left:1.5em;">
<ul>
<li>Costantino Bresciani-Turroni, <i>The Economics of Inflation</i> (English transl.). Northampton, England: Augustus Kelly Publishers, 1937, on the German 1919-1923 inflation.</li>
<li>Shun-Hsin Chou, <i>The Chinese Inflation 1937-1949</i>, New York, Columbia University Press, 1963, Library of Congress Cat. 62-18260.</li>
<li>Andrew Dickson White, <i>Fiat Money Inflation in France</i>, Caxton Printers, Idaho, 1969. a popular description of the 1789-1799 inflation.</li>
</ul>
</div>
<p><a name="External_links" id="External_links"></a></p>
